  "design_notes": [
    "Two parallel Scope/ScopeManager hierarchies: OpenTelemetry (ScopeInterface) and DDTrace (Contracts\\Scope / DDTrace\\Contracts\\ScopeManager)",
    "OpenTelemetry Context is immutable: with() and withContextValue() return new instances",
    "DDTrace ScopeManager maintains a stack; deactivate() restores the previous active scope",
    "Scope.close() optionally finishes the wrapped Span (finishSpanOnClose flag)",
    "LoggingTrait provides structured debug/warn/error logging to DDTrace classes"
